<paragraph id="IFRS17_3" base="F55665976"><paranum>3</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 17"/><data name="paranum" value="3"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS17_P0017">An entity shall apply IFRS 17 to: </p><ol id="IFRS17_L0003" base="F55665978" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IFRS17_P0018" base="F55665979"><xref base="F55666957" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0532">insurance contracts<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0186"/></ph></xref>, including <xref base="F55667022" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0554"><i>reinsurance contracts</i><ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0323"/></ph></xref>, it issues;</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IFRS17_P0019" base="F55665981">reinsurance contracts it holds; and</p></li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value> <p id="IFRS17_P0020" base="F55665983"><xref base="F55666988" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0543"><i>investment contracts with discretionary participation features</i><ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0204"/></ph></xref> it issues, provided the entity also issues insurance contracts. </p></li></ol></body></paragraph>